author: Source: Bicester Advertiser
title: England sweat on virus victim Ben Stokes ahead of second Test against Pakistan - Bicester Advertiser
text:
England may have to make a last-minute call on Ben Stokes' fitness, as he tries to recover from a stomach bug in time for the second Test against Pakistan. Stokes missed training on Tuesday, but was set to take a full part at nets on the eve of the Test at the Dubai International Cricket Stadium.
 Bicester Advertiser.
